 tanker tonne-miles), a range of developments have weighed on buyer demand for Russian cargoes recently. However, with geo-political ‘turbulence’ still highly in focus, there could be further shifts ahead for this key trade flow. ","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-26T09:43:18","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Thomas Rowley"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221542","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":844,"ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Oil and Tanker Trades Outlook","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":44994,"Description":"Thomas Rowley","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F188244.jpg","RecordAdded":"2026-02-26T09:43:18","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":44995,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F221542%2F2026-02-26_upload_6864782_OTTO_02_2026.png","RecordAdded":"2026-02-26T09:43:18","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221553,"Title":"LPG Carrier Market Outlook - February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"The VLGC spot market remained historically firm in January and into February amid robust export volumes and a supportive arbitrage whilst 2026 is shaping up to be another positive year for LPG carrier markets, with headline fundamentals supportive. Nevertheless, impacts from robust deliveries are expected to build in 