rting Asia EB, 14dma","Type":6,"Title":"China-US Containership Tracker – 6-17k TEU Ships Departing Asia Eastbound Across Pacific, 14dma","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":8852030,"TimeseriesSortOrder":22,"ArticleId":221441,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: M, Unit: Knots","Type":6,"Title":"Containership Average Speed","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":551620,"TimeseriesSortOrder":23,"ArticleId":221441,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: TEU","Type":6,"Title":"Total Containership Gulf of Aden Vessel Arrivals","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221374,"Title":"US Supreme Court Ruling on US Tariffs - 22nd February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"After the US Supreme Court stuck down most tariffs implemented last year, the US President has announced a new temporary import tariff of 15% on all trade partners under a separate legal framework.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-22T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221374","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221377,"Title":"Sizing Up Containership Operators’ Ownership Swing","Content":"","Synopsis":"The exceptional container markets of recent years have given liner companies an opportunity to drive a major wave of growth in the fleet and build an increasingly dominant ownership position in the sector. With operators now owning twice as much tonnage as charter owners, we take a look at the drivers of this shift and the potential implications ahead…","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-20T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"David Whittaker"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221377","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":221377,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":845,"ArticleId":221377,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Intelligence Weekly","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":221377,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":44929,"Description":"David Whittaker","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F114552.jpg","RecordAdded":"2026-02-23T09:07:20","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":221377,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":44930,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F221377%2F2026-02-23_upload_9114552_SIW%201712.png","RecordAdded":"2026-02-23T09:07:20","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":221377,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":530258,"TimeseriesSortOrder":1,"ArticleId":221377,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: M, Unit: TEU thousand, Total Container Operator Owner Flt Dev","Type":6,"Title":"Total Containership Operator Owner Fleet Development","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":53