hand Prices","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221542,"Title":"Indian Crude Imports: Evolving Once More?","Content":"","Synopsis":"While Indian imports of Russian crude have been elevated since the onset of the Russia-Ukraine conflict (providing significant upside for tanker tonne-miles), a range of developments have weighed on buyer demand for Russian cargoes recently. However, with geo-political ‘turbulence’ still highly in focus, there could be further shifts ahead for this key trade flow. ","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-26T09:43:18","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Thomas Rowley"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221542","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":844,"ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Oil and Tanker Trades Outlook","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":44994,"Description":"Thomas Rowley","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F188244.jpg","RecordAdded":"2026-02-26T09:43:18","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":44995,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F221542%2F2026-02-26_upload_6864782_OTTO_02_2026.png","RecordAdded":"2026-02-26T09:43:18","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":221542,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221553,"Title":"LPG Carrier Market Outlook - February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"The VLGC spot market remained historically firm in January and into February amid robust export volumes and a supportive arbitrage whilst 2026 is shaping up to be another positive year for LPG carrier markets, with headline fundamentals supportive. Nevertheless, impacts from robust deliveries are expected to build in 2027.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-26T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221553","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":696,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"LPG Carrier","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1463,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Sector Outlook","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":30451,"TimeseriesSortOrder":20,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":"(SIN, SV) Freq: A, Unit: No","Type":6,"Title":"Total LPG Demolition","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":30452,"TimeseriesSortOrder":21,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":"(SIN, SV) Freq: A, Unit: ,000 Cu. M.","Type":6,"Title":"Total LPG Demolition","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":49623,"TimeseriesSortOrder":18,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":"(SIN, SV) Freq: A, Unit: No, LPG Contracts","Type":6,"Title":"LPG Contracting","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":49691,"TimeseriesSortOrder":19,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":"(SIN, SV) Freq: A, Unit: Cu. M., LPG Contracts","Type":6,"Title":"LPG Contracting","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":98803,"TimeseriesSortOrder":4,"ArticleId":221553,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: Million Tonnes","Type":6,"Title":