 at ~$60,000/day since late January (the highest levels since March 2023) amidst a 'red-hot' VLCC market, with spot earnings nearing the $200,000/day mark in late February.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-26T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221550","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1000,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Entity Type","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1010,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Structures","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":617,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1004,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Output Type","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1428,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Website","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":97725,"TimeseriesSortOrder":1,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: W, Unit: $/day","Type":6,"Title":"Clarksons Average Tanker Earnings","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":543935,"TimeseriesSortOrder":2,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, SV) Freq: W, Unit: $/day, Average VLCC c.2015 Scrubber Earnings","Type":6,"Title":"Average VLCC c. 2015-built (Eco) Scrubber-Fitted Earnings","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":546177,"TimeseriesSortOrder":3,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: W, Unit: $/day","Type":6,"Title":"Average Weighted Crude Tanker Earnings","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":546185,"TimeseriesSortOrder":4,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: W, Unit: $/day","Type":6,"Title":"Average Weighted Product Tanker Earnings","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":33326,"TimeseriesSortOrder":5,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: No","Type":6,"Title":"VLCC Sales","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":548623,"TimeseriesSortOrder":6,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: % Yr/Yr (mbpd)","Type":6,"Title":"World Seaborne Crude Oil Trade","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":534497,"TimeseriesSortOrder":7,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: % Yr/Yr","Type":6,"Title":"Crude Tanker Fleet Growth","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":549056,"TimeseriesSortOrder":8,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: % Yr/Yr","Type":6,"Title":"Product Tanker Trading Fleet Growth","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":542419,"TimeseriesSortOrder":9,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: % Yr/Yr","Type":6,"Title":"Total Tanker Fleet Growth","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221441,"Title":"Containership Market Outlook - February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"Container shipping markets continued to see mixed trends into February, with the timecharter market remaining exceptionally firm, while freight rates have continued to soften; underlying sector fundamentals could see a weaker period for markets ahead, but uncertainties around Red Sea re-routing, US trade policy, and wider geopolitics remain in sharp focus.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-24T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221441","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":221441,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":104