its","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12792864,"TimeseriesSortOrder":4,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: No, Total Crude Tanker Strait of Hormuz Transits","Type":6,"Title":"Strait of Hormuz Transits > Crude Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12792949,"TimeseriesSortOrder":5,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: No, Total Products Tanker Strait of Hormuz Transits","Type":6,"Title":"Strait of Hormuz Transits > Products Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12792761,"TimeseriesSortOrder":6,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: No, Total Bulkcarrier Strait of Hormuz Transits","Type":6,"Title":"Strait of Hormuz Transits > Bulkcarrier","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12792969,"TimeseriesSortOrder":7,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: No, Total Containership Strait of Hormuz Transits","Type":6,"Title":"Strait of Hormuz Transits > Containership","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":98359,"TimeseriesSortOrder":8,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: mbpd, Iran Seaborne Crude Exp","Type":6,"Title":"Iran Seaborne Crude Oil Exports","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":548152,"TimeseriesSortOrder":9,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN, WOR, OIN, RIN) Freq: W, Unit: $/bbl","Type":6,"Title":"Brent Crude Oil Price, 1 Month Future","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":543847,"TimeseriesSortOrder":10,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: W, Unit: $/day, VLCC c.2015 AG-Ningbo Scrubber Earnings","Type":6,"Title":"VLCC c. 2015-built (Eco) Ras Tanura - Ningbo Scrubber-Fitted Earnings","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":555955,"TimeseriesSortOrder":11,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: GT million","Type":6,"Title":"Total Gulf of Aden Vessel Arrivals, 7dma","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":551280,"TimeseriesSortOrder":12,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: Number","Type":6,"Title":"Total Gulf of Aden Vessel Arrivals","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":556700,"TimeseriesSortOrder":13,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: D, Unit: Number","Type":6,"Title":"Total Strait of Hormuz Vessel Arrivals","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":974,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"c464b4da-297b-49ee-b58b-35330e28b5c0","Location":"Middle East Conflict 1st March 2026.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":221669,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"Middle East Conflict 1st March 2026.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221374,"Title":"US Supreme Court Ruling on US Tariffs - 22nd February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"After the US Supreme Court stuck down most tariffs implemented last year, the US President has announced a new temporary import tariff of 15% on all trade partners under a separate legal framework.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-22T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221374","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221250,"Title":"Monthly Offshore Renewables Highlights - February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"Challenges in the offshore wind sector have resulted in a meaningful slowdown in project investment, though 2026 has the potential to be more positive, with $48bn projected to be invested globally (+21% y-o-y). Meanwhile in the 'wind' vessel markets, C/SOV and CTV rates have picked up ahead of summer, with C/SOV charter rates averaging ~€50,000/day in Europe, reflecting expectations of another tight market and limited vessel availability across the coming summer.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-18T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221250","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1450,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Wind","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1463,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Sector Outlook","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1451,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"RIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":221250,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":10318751,"TimeseriesSortOrder":1,"ArticleId":221250,"Summary":"(WOR, OIN, RIN) Freq: A, Unit: Capacity (GW), Active > Renewables > Wind Farms, Active > Renewables > Wind Farms","Type":6,"Title":"Active > Wind Farms","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":10318762,"TimeseriesSortOrder":2,"ArticleId":221250,"Summary":"(WOR, OIN, RIN) Freq: A, Unit: Capacity (GW), In Development > Renewables > Wind Farms, In Development > Renewables > Wind Farms","Type":6,"Title":"Start-Ups > Wind Farms","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":10336220,"TimeseriesSortOrder":3,"ArticleId":221250,"Summary":"(RIN) Freq: A, Unit: $m","Type":6,"Title":"FID > Offshore Wind Investment (With Forecast)","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":558428,"TimeseriesSortOrder":4,"ArticleId":221250,"Summary":"(RIN) Freq: M, Unit: €/Day","Type":6,"Title":"CSOV, 120 Pax, 3-9 Month Charter, Europe, Mid-Point","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":903792,"TimeseriesSortOrder":5,"ArticleId":221250,"Summary":"(RIN) Freq: M, Unit: €/Day","Type":6,"Title":"WTIV Charter Rates, 4th Generation, Mid-Point","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221249,"Title":"Hapag-Lloyd - ZIM Merger Agreement: Overview &amp; Context - 18th February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"February 16th saw Hapag-Lloyd sign a merger agreement with ZIM. The deal is set to solidify Hapag Lloyd's status as the world's fifth largest operator, and could most notably impact container shipping on the Transpacific.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-18T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221249","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":971,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"43fe065d-e5d4-4cd6-9de8-3a55efac1eef","Location":"Hapag Lloyd ZIM Merger February 2026.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"Hapag Lloyd ZIM Merger February 2026.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":221140,"Title":"US Maritime Action Plan: Summary of Proposals - 15th February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"On 13th Feb, the US Government published its ‘Maritime Action Plan’, providing more detail on planned policy actions to revitalise the US maritime industry. Potential policies include fees for foreign-built vessels carrying imports into the US, investment in US shipyards and the broader maritime supply chain, maritime workforce training and the creation of a US flagged strategic commercial fleet.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-15T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/221140","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1430,"ArticleId":221140,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"WFR","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":833,"ArticleId":221140,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"World Fleet Monitor","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":969,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"b7ff5c93-4326-40c9-b6bc-fe8997002bde","Location":"US Maritime Action Plan 15022026.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"US Maritime Action Plan 15022026.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":220861,"Title":"Sanctioned Vessel &amp; Oil Trade Flows Overview: February 2026","Content":"","Synopsis":"Following further expansion of US sanctions against Iran, the count of tankers specifically listed as sanctioned has increased to 934 oil tankers and 112m dwt, 16% of global tanker fleet capacity, with recent impacts of sanctions and geo-politics on oil trade flows increasing “mainstream” tanker demand.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2026-02-09T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Stephen Gordon"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/220861","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":617,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1430,"ArticleId":220861,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"WFR","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":833,"ArticleId":220861,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"World Fleet Monitor","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":0,"Description":null,"Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F18376.jpg","RecordAdded":null,"Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12110694,"TimeseriesSortOrder":1,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: No., Sanctioned Oil Tanker Fleet Development","Type":6,"Title":"Sanctioned Fleet Development > Oil Tankers","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12110690,"TimeseriesSortOrder":2,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: DWT, Sanct