p","Type":6,"Title":"Venezuela Seaborne Crude Oil Exports","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":24316,"TimeseriesSortOrder":2,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: M, Unit: mbpd","Type":6,"Title":"Global Oil Prod.","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":219128,"Title":"US Seizes Second Tanker Off Venezuela: Overview &amp; Context","Content":"","Synopsis":"The US has intensified pressure on Venezuela in recent days, with US forces seizing a second tanker while reports suggest that they are seeking to board a third vessel.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-12-22T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/219128","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":617,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":219128,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":219128,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":219128,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":534169,"TimeseriesSortOrder":1,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN) Freq: A, Unit: Million Tonnes, Venezuela Crude Exp","Type":6,"Title":"Venezuela Seaborne Crude Oil Exports","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12110694,"TimeseriesSortOrder":2,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: No., Sanctioned Oil Tanker Fleet Development","Type":6,"Title":"Sanctioned Fleet Development > Oil Tankers","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":557261,"TimeseriesSortOrder":3,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: % Fleet (DWT), Sanctioned Oil Tanker Fleet Development","Type":6,"Title":"Sanctioned Fleet Development > Oil Tankers","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":218625,"Title":"US Seizes Tanker Off Venezuelan Coast: Overview &amp; Context","Content":"","Synopsis":"The US seized a sanctioned oil tanker off the coast of Venezuela on Wednesday, marking a further escalation in tensions between the two countries with a range of implications on oil trade flows and tanker markets possible going forward.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-12-11T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/218625","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":218625,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":218625,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":218625,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":617,"ArticleId":218625,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12110694,"TimeseriesSortOrder":1,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: No., Sanctioned Oil Tanker Fleet Development","Type":6,"Title":"Sanctioned Fleet Development > Oil Tankers","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":12110690,"TimeseriesSortOrder":2,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: DWT, Sanctioned Oil Tanker Fleet Development","Type":6,"Title":"Sanctioned Fleet Development > Oil Tankers","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":557254,"TimeseriesSortOrder":3,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, WFR) Freq: D, Unit: % Fleet (DWT), Sanctioned Crude Tanker Fleet Development","Type":6,"Title":"Sanctioned Fleet Development > Crude Tankers","MatchCount":null},{"TsSeriesId":69918,"TimeseriesSortOrder":4,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":"(SIN, SV) Freq: W, Unit: $/day, VLCC Avg Earn (Long Series)","Type":6,"Title":"Average VLCC Long Run Historical Earnings","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":217255,"Title":"‘Trade War Truce’: US-China Tensions Ease For Now","Content":"","Synopsis":"This week’s “trade war truce” has stabilised US-Chinese relations (for now), brought positive implications for seaborne trade flows (e.g. soybeans) and eased some operational challenges (e.g. suspension of port fees, two weeks after introduction). In our Analysis we recap on this further example of the “fluid” nature of US policy and ongoing negotiations between the world’s largest economies.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-10-31T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Stephen Gordon"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/217255","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":10,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipbuilding & Repair","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":617,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Tanker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":625,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Bulker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":626,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Gas Carrier","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":845,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Intelligence Weekly","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1430,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"WFR","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":43097,"Description":"Stephen Gordon","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F18376.jpg","RecordAdded":"2025-10-31T17:56:28","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":43098,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F217255%2F2025-10-31_upload_5481104_SIW%201697.png","RecordAdded":"2025-10-31T17:56:28","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":217255,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":217187,"Title":"US-China Policy: 30th Oct 2025 Update","Content":"","Synopsis":"The announcement of a one year 'truce' between the US and China eases some of the recent trade tensions and disruption for maritime. US tariffs on imports from China will be lowered, while both the US and China have agreed to suspend recently introduced port fees.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-10-30T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/217187","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1240,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"China P.R.","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":217187,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":930,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"23fef358-0c91-4560-ad95-79452a7bff80","Location":"US-China Policy Update 30 Oct 2025.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"US-China Policy Update 30 Oct 2025.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":216926,"Title":"US-China Grain Trade: Geopolitics Back In Focus","Content":"","Synopsis":"More than 5 years after the last ‘trade war’, grain trade is once again caught in the crossfire of US-China trade tensions. As we head into Q4, US farmers would typically be starting to ramp-up their shipments of soybeans to buyers, with China traditionally dominating, but this year is looking anything but typical, with Chinese buyers avoiding US purchases and creating an uncertain outlook...","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-10-23T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"David Whittaker"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/216926","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":625,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Bulker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":838,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Dry Bulk Trade Outlook","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":42957,"Description":"David Whittaker","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F114552.jpg","RecordAdded":"2025-10-23T13:59:08","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":42958,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F216926%2F2025-10-23_upload_7299602_DBTO2510.png","RecordAdded":"2025-10-23T13:59:08","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":216926,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":216732,"Title":"US And Chinese Port Fees: Taking Stock...","Content":"","Synopsis":"Shipping has again it seems been at the “frontline” of geo-politics this week, with US port fees on Chinese related vessels commencing, rapid introduction of Chinese “counter measures” and heated discussions at IMO around the pace and direction of emissions reduction. In this week’s Analysis, we try to take stock after a “chaotic” week, aiming to provide a framework for assessing impacts.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-10-17T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Stephen Gordon"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/216732","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":10,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipbuilding & Repair","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":625,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Bulker","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":626,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Gas Carrier","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":845,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Intelligence Weekly","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1430,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"WFR","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":42897,"Description":"Stephen Gordon","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F18376.jpg","RecordAdded":"2025-10-17T19:18:29","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":42898,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F216732%2F2025-10-17_upload_9194772_SIW%201695.png","RecordAdded":"2025-10-17T19:18:29","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":927,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"11208284-f5f4-4874-9ea1-e0ea33178c5c","Location":"Chinese Port Fees Update No 3 - Oct 2025.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":216732,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"Chinese Port Fees Update No 3 - Oct 2025.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":215075,"Title":"US Policy: Maritime Impact Tracker (August 2025)","Content":"","Synopsis":"This is the third edition of our US Policy Maritime Tracker, which draws on our coverage of US policy developments and its maritime impacts, including a summary of key data points and a selection of key charts that support the tracking of trends influenced by US policy changes.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-08-29T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/215075","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":215075,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":908,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"ca55d107-6d3e-4333-af5b-0517036f491f","Location":"US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker 29 August 2025.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker 29 August 2025.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":214570,"Title":"Car Carriers: Resilient (For Now) Amid Disruption","Content":"","Synopsis":"US tariffs have been at the top of the agenda in the car carrier sector (and the wider car industry) this year, and while some impacts have emerged, trade volumes have held up fairly well so far. Car carrier markets have also shown some resilience of late as they continue to gradually normalise after a record run, although a range of complex factors are shaping the outlook...","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-08-15T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"David Whittaker"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/214570","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":629,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Pure Car Carrier","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":845,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Intelligence Weekly","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1001,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Subject Type","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1002,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Geographical Area","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1428,"ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Website","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":42099,"Description":"David Whittaker","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F114552.jpg","RecordAdded":"2025-08-15T14:36:55","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":42100,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F214570%2F2025-08-15_upload_8956202_SIW%201686.png","RecordAdded":"2025-08-15T14:36:55","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":214570,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":214204,"Title":"US Policy: Tariffs &amp; Deals","Content":"","Synopsis":"With the 90 day “pause” on proposed higher US import tariffs expiring yesterday, in this week’s Analysis we re-cap on the current position, review progress made on “deals” and discuss shipping market impacts and the uncertainties that remain. And across the 464mt and 3.6% of seaborne trade freshly tariffed this year, there is plenty of detail and complexity to track.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-08-01T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Stephen Gordon"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/214204","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleE