olicy: Maritime Impact Tracker (July 2025)","Content":"","Synopsis":"This is the second edition of our US Policy Maritime Tracker, which draws on our coverage of US policy developments and its maritime impacts, including a summary of key data points and a selection of key charts that support the tracking of trends influenced by US policy changes.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-07-22T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/213778","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":894,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"d4573bc0-cc91-4e18-9b2c-c5a33a124f21","Location":"US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker - July 2025.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker - July 2025.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":213017,"Title":"Transpacific Container Trade: A Volatile Year So Far","Content":"","Synopsis":"Amid the notably ‘fluid’ US trade policy seen throughout 2025, the container sector, and particularly the Transpacific, have been sharply in focus. In this month’s Container Commentary, we take a look at the four key ‘phases’ of volatility (so far) that have emerged on the Transpacific trade lane as a result of significant ‘shifts’ in US trade policy this year...","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-06-25T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Thomas Grant"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/213017","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":837,"ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Container Intelligence Monthly","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":41534,"Description":"Thomas Grant","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F167501.jpg","RecordAdded":"2025-06-25T11:16:28","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":41535,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Image&FileName=Articles%2F213017%2F2025-06-25_upload_4960047_CIM%202506.png","RecordAdded":"2025-06-25T11:16:28","Usage":"Main Image","ArticleId":213017,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":212661,"Title":"US Policy: Maritime Impact Tracker (Jun 2025)","Content":"","Synopsis":"Drawing on our coverage of US policy developments and its maritime impacts, we have created a US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker, including a summary of key data points and a selection of key charts that support the tracking of trends influenced by US policy changes.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-06-13T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Clarksons Research"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/212661","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":859,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"94b553dc-c201-4084-af4b-ffdc3dd0577e","Location":"US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker 13 June 2025.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"US Policy Maritime Impact Tracker 13 June 2025.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":212548,"Title":"USTR Measures: Chinese Vessels &amp; Shipbuilding - Update No 3, June 2025","Content":"","Synopsis":"The USTR has proposed changes to its Section 301 measures relating to Chinese-linked ships, proposing a reduction in US port fees for foreign-built car carriers and changes to the regulatory framework impacting LNG carriers.","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-06-11T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"Stephen Gordon"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/212548","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1042,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Briefings","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":10,"ArticleId":212548,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipbuilding & Repair","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":212548,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1430,"ArticleId":212548,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"WFR","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":212548,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":0,"Description":null,"Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F18376.jpg","RecordAdded":null,"Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":0,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleDocumentLinkId":null,"ArticleDocumentId":857,"ArticleDocumentGuid":"0c88f9d7-ef73-4cb0-829c-ba93106543b5","Location":"USTR Measures - Chinese Vessels %26 Shipbuilding Update No 3 - Jun 2025.pdf","CreatedDate":null,"DeleteStatus":false,"ArticleId":212548,"Summary":null,"Type":8,"Title":"USTR Measures - Chinese Vessels %26 Shipbuilding Update No 3 - Jun 2025.pdf","MatchCount":null}],"RelatedArticles":null},{"ArticleId":212188,"Title":"US Policy: Tracking Transpacific Container Trends","Content":"","Synopsis":"The container sector is amongst the most exposed parts of shipping to recent shifts in US trade policy, with the Transpacific particularly in focus as China-US container volumes have been buffeted by new tariffs. With US policy ‘fluid’, and with impacts volatile and uneven, keeping a close eye on the latest trends is important; here we run down a selection of indicators to track...","KeyWords":null,"LastUpdated":"0001-01-01T00:00:00","PublishedOn":"2025-05-30T00:00:00","UseContentForSynopsis":false,"Authors":[{"Name":"David Whittaker"}],"Url":"https://sin.clarksons.net/News/Article/212188","RoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","DocumentLinkRoleRestrictionsJson":"{\"DefaultRestriction\": \"Show\"}","IsSticky":false,"HasContent":true,"ArticleTemplateId":null,"RequiresTrialistOrSubscriberAccess":true,"IsPublished":0,"ArticleEntityLinks":[{"CategoryId":627,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Containership","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":845,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Intelligence Weekly","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1041,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Analysis","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":12,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Shipping Related","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1486,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"Policy","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1412,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"United States","MatchCount":null},{"CategoryId":1429,"ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":1,"Title":"SIN","MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":41253,"Description":"David Whittaker","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/News/GetImage?Type=Thumbnail&FileName=EmployeePhotos%2F114552.jpg","RecordAdded":"2025-05-30T19:04:22","Usage":"Thumbnail","ArticleId":212188,"Summary":null,"Type":3,"Title":null,"MatchCount":null},{"ArticleImageLinkId":41254,"Description":"Backpage Image","Height":null,"Width":null,"Location":"/